---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
import Nav from '../../components/Nav.astro'
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Layout
  title="Legal Notice · CrossFit La Mola"
  description="Legal notice and terms of use for the CrossFit La Mola website, Terrassa. Owner information, intellectual property, liabilities and jurisdiction under Spanish LSSI-CE law."
>
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <style>
      .legal-content{ max-width:780px; margin:0 auto;}
      .legal-content h2{ font-family:var(--f-display); font-weight:600; font-size:clamp(22px,2.5vw,28px); margin:48px 0 16px; letter-spacing:-0.02em;}
      .legal-content h3{ font-family:var(--f-display); font-weight:500; font-size:18px; margin:32px 0 12px;}
      .legal-content p, .legal-content li{ font-family:var(--f-serif); font-size:17px; line-height:1.7; color:var(--bone-2); margin:0 0 16px;}
      .legal-content ul{ padding-left:24px; margin:0 0 20px;}
      .legal-content li{ margin-bottom:8px;}
      .legal-content a{ color:var(--accent-hi); text-decoration:underline;}
      .legal-content strong{ color:var(--bone); font-weight:500;}
    </style>
  </Fragment>

  <Nav />

  <section class="page-hero" style="min-height:40svh">
    <div class="bg" style="background:#1a1814"></div>
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="crumb"><a href="/en">Home</a><span>/</span><span>Legal notice</span></div>
      <h1>Legal<br><em class="serif">notice</em><span class="dot">.</span></h1>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="sec ink">
    <div class="inner legal-content">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> April 2025</p>

      <h2>1. General information</h2>
      <p>In compliance with Article 10 of Law 34/2002, of July 11, on Information Society Services and Electronic Commerce (LSSICE), the following is provided:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Owner:</strong> CrossFit La Mola</li>
        <li><strong>Address:</strong> Av. del Vallès 724C, 08227 Terrassa, Barcelona, Spain</li>
        <li><strong>Email:</strong> hola@crossfitlamola.com</li>
        <li><strong>Phone:</strong> +34 629 06 65 31</li>
        <li><strong>Activity:</strong> Sports center specialized in CrossFit</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Purpose</h2>
      <p>This website aims to provide information about CrossFit La Mola's services, including classes, schedules, rates, and contact details.</p>

      <h2>3. Terms of use</h2>
      <p>Access and use of this website grants the status of user and implies acceptance of these terms. The user agrees to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Make lawful use of the website, in accordance with current legislation</li>
        <li>Not engage in activities that may damage, disable, or overload the website</li>
        <li>Not introduce viruses or malicious software</li>
        <li>Respect intellectual property rights</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Intellectual property</h2>
      <p>All content on this website (texts, images, logos, design, source code) is the property of CrossFit La Mola or its legitimate owners, and is protected by intellectual property legislation.</p>
      <p>The "CrossFit" trademark is owned by CrossFit, LLC. CrossFit La Mola is an affiliated box licensed to use the brand.</p>
      <p>Reproduction, distribution, or modification of the content without express authorization is prohibited.</p>

      <h2>5. Disclaimer</h2>
      <p>CrossFit La Mola is not responsible for:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>Errors or omissions in the website content</li>
        <li>The availability and continuity of the website</li>
        <li>Damages caused by viruses or malicious software</li>
        <li>Improper use of the website by users</li>
        <li>Content of third-party websites that may be accessed through links</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>6. External links</h2>
      <p>This website may contain links to third-party websites. CrossFit La Mola does not control these sites and is not responsible for their content or privacy policies.</p>

      <h2>7. Modifications</h2>
      <p>CrossFit La Mola reserves the right to modify the website content and these terms of use at any time without prior notice.</p>

