      <p>These terms are governed by Spanish law. For any dispute, the parties submit to the courts of Terrassa, expressly waiving any other jurisdiction that may apply.</p>

      <h2>9. Contact</h2>
      <p>For any questions about this legal notice, you can contact us at <a href="mailto:hola@crossfitlamola.com">hola@crossfitlamola.com</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
